verbose_text: Amount of N 2 -fixed = (% Ndfa x Total N legume)/100Where Total N legume is the% N in the legume plant times the dry biomass yield of the legume plant.Net N input = Total amount of N 2 -fixed - Total amount of N removed in grain The total amount of N 2 -fixed includes the N content in the below-ground parts, estimated at 30% of the amount of N 2 -fixed in the shoots.
